description: Construction of 845sqm (GIA) community centre (use class D2); 394sqm (GIA) nursery school (use class D1); 55 affordable dwellings (use class C3) consisting of a tenure of; - 27 units consisting of: 6no. 1-bed, 1no. 2-bed, 19no. 3-bed, and 1no. 4-bed to be provided at 'London Affordable Rent' and,  - 28 units consisting of: 13no. 1-bed and 15no. 2-bed to be provided at 'London Shared Ownership' and; landscape and public realm improvements; new and replacement car parking arrangements; new pedestrian access routes; and all associated infrastructure, including an electrical substation.
